updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"created":"2008-04-15T03:18:41.958+0000","updated":"2008-04-15T03:18:41.958+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12393953/comment/12588886","id":"12588886","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"body":"This patch changes numRequests, numErrors, and totalTime to AtomicLongs.  It also changes the casting in the calculation of avgRequestsPerSecond.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"created":"2008-04-15T03:19:25.758+0000","updated":"2008-04-15T03:19:25.758+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12393953/comment/12589111","id":"12589111","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"body":"I don't know that I explained the problem with the calculation of avgRequestsPerSecond well.  Here is a code snippet that illustrates the problem:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\npublic class CastingTest {\r\n  public static void main(String args[]) throws Exception{\r\n    long t1 = System.currentTimeMillis();\r\n    long t2 = t1 + 7456L;\r\n    System.out.println(\"Cast then subtract: \" + ((float)t2 - t1));\r\n    System.out.println(\"Subtract then cast: \" + (float)(t2 - t1));\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nOutput:\r\n{noformat}\r\n% java CastingTest\r\nCast then subtract: 0.0\r\nSubtract then cast: 7456.0\r\n{noformat}\r\n\r\nSo, at least shortly after start up, the way the casting is currently done results in a divide by zero.\r\n\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"created":"2008-04-15T14:58:44.254+0000","updated":"2008-04-15T14:58:44.254+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12393953/comment/12591506","id":"12591506","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"body":"Here is an illustration of the divide by zero bug.  Notice the value of avgRequestsPerSecond.  This is two minutes after server start.\r\n\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nstats: \trequests : 4255\r\n        errors : 0\r\n        avgTimePerRequest : 196.68672\r\n        avgRequestsPerSecond : Infinity\r\n{code}","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=timmsc","name":"timmsc","emailAddress":"TimmSC at aol dot com","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Sean Timm","active":true},"created":"2008-04-23T01:27:15.112+0000","updated":"2008-04-23T01:27:15.112+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12393953/comment/12598888","id":"12598888","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=otis","name":"otis","emailAddress":"otis at apache dot org","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859"},"displayName":"Otis Gospodnetic","active":true},"body":"Merci.  I applied the volatile variation.\r\n\r\nCommitted revision 658977.\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=otis","name":"otis","emailAddress":"otis at apache dot org","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=otis&avatarId=15859"},"displayName":"Otis Gospodnetic","active":true},"created":"2008-05-22T02:13:29.542+0000","updated":"2008-05-22T02:13:29.542+0000"}]},"votes":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/SOLR-539/votes","votes":0,"hasVoted":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_12311820":"0|i03w6v:"}}